<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
        <meta name="description" content="">
        <!-- favicon -->
        <!--<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png">
        <link rel="manifest" href="/favicon/site.webmanifest">-->
        
        <!-- Import CSS Bootstrap -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <!-- Import custom CSS -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style-music.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style-navbar.css">

        <title>Another Light Out - Armel Rouxel</title>
    </head>
 
    <body>
        <header>
        </header>
        <main>
            <div class="background another-light-out"></div>
            <a href="/music" class="link-tab"> < Page principale</a>
            <div class="header container">
                <div class="row align-items-center h-100">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center">
                            <span class="head-title text-center">Another Light Out</span>
                        </div> 
                        <div class="row justify-content-center">
                            <span class="head-subtitle">Juin 2021</span>
                        </div> 
                        <div class="row justify-content-center mt-4">
                            <a href="https://ffm.to/xbk0vry" target="_blank" class="btn btn-cart" role="button" name="add-cart"><i class="fas fa-play pr-2"></i> Écouter</a>
                            <a href="/music/makingof_reach_that_light_out" class="btn btn-cart ml-3" role="button" name="add-cart"><i class="fas fa-search pr-2"></i> Making-Of </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row m-0">
                    <div class="col-md-5 p-0">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/another_light_out/cover.jpg">
                    </div>
                    <div class="album-desc col-md-7 pl-md-5 p-0 mt-4 mt-md-0">
                        <div class="row m-0">
                            <span class="title">À propos de Another Light Out ...</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="album-about row m-0 pt-2">
                            <p>
                                Another Light Out fait figure de "suite" à mon premier album "Reach That Light", il contient toutes les musiques et idées non utilisées ou achevée à la sortie de l'album.<br/>
                                Par exemple, "And So It Ends" est la musique pûrement électronique que je voulais créer pour l'album sans succès, se retrouvant simplement sous l'aspect de morceau de transition. C'est aussi le projet ou j'ai pu tester mon clavier nouvellement acquis ainsi que divers nouveaux sons.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                La couleur y est beaucoup plus claire et l'ambience plus chaude que pour l'album principal. En effet, j'ai voulu mettre une sorte de résolution à la thématique qui y était développée. Le personnage arrête de lutter et se laisse enfin aller, le tout dans une mélancolie nostalgique.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row m-0 mt-4">
                    <div class="col-md-5 p-0">
                        <div class="row m-0">
                            <span class="title">Écouter l'EP</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row m-0 pt-2">
                            <iframe src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/3JVd4bNE64geWvl7Yvbkqv?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="380" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"></iframe>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="album-desc col-md-7 pl-md-5 p-0 mt-4 mt-md-0">
                        <div class="row m-0">
                            <span class="title">Photos</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row m-0">
                            <div class="gallery col p-0">
                                <div class="row m-0">
                                    <% for (var i=0; i < gallery.length; i++) { %>
                                        <div class="col-md-3 col-4 p-2" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#galleryModal" data-i="<%= i %>">
                                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/another_light_out/<%= gallery[i] %>">
                                        </div>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer"></div>

            <!-- ==================================== MODAL =================================== -->

            <div class="modal fade " id="galleryModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="galleryLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="col modal-body" style="text-transform:none; font-weight: 500;">
                            <!--<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close" style="position: absolute;right: 15px;top: 10px;z-index: 1;">
                                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                            </button>-->
                            
                            <div class="row m-0">
                                <div class="carousel-container d-flex">
                                    <div id="carouselGallery" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                                        <% for (var i=0; i < gallery.length; i++) { %>
                                            <div class="carousel-item <% if (!i) { %> active <% } %>">
                                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/another_light_out/<%= gallery[i] %>">
                                            </div>
                                        <% } %>
                                        </div>
                                        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselGallery" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                                        </a>
                                        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselGallery" role="button" data-slide="next">
                                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </body>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- Import Font Awesome -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/5f21f19d3f.js"></script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        // On gère les carousels
        $('div[data-target="#galleryModal"]').on('click', function (data) {
            $(`#carouselGallery .carousel-item`).removeClass('active');
            let i = parseInt($(data.currentTarget).attr('data-i'));
            console.log(`#carouselGallery .carousel-item:nth-child(${i+1})`);
            $(`#carouselGallery .carousel-item:nth-child(${i+1})`).addClass('active');
        })
    </script>
</html>